overview: The user initiated a review of their sleep questionnaire application
  to verify its adherence to the project's acceptance criteria. The assistant
  performed a comprehensive analysis, identifying both fulfilled requirements
  and significant gaps in functionality. A detailed plan was then formulated,
  prioritizing the missing features. The assistant has since begun implementing
  this plan, successfully integrating a 1-10 severity scale for tiredness,
  complete with dynamic safety warnings in both the interactive questionnaire
  and the generated PDF report. Additionally, the logic for detecting Comorbid
  Insomnia and Sleep Apnea (COMISA) has been added. The project is currently in
  progress, with further enhancements planned to address remaining identified
  issues.
